WEBVTT

00:00:08.40 --> 00:00:09.40
Hey!

00:00:09.80 --> 00:00:10.30
My name is Xavier

0:00:11.80 --> 0:00:13.40
and I'm a car enthusiast.

0:00:13.90 --> 0:00:15.50
I enjoy anything car related

0:00:16.00 --> 0:00:18.10
whether it's basic maintenance

0:00:18.60 --> 0:00:20.60
like a simple tire rotation

0:00:21.10 --> 0:00:22.80
or custom modifications

0:00:23.20 --> 0:00:24.60
like an air intake system.

0:00:26.00 --> 0:00:28.50
This is my 2015 Honda Civic EX. 

0:00:29.00 --> 0:00:30.60 
It may not be the quickest car

0:00:31.10 --> 0:00:33.50
but it's been nothing short of amazing.

0:00:34.00 --> 0:00:35.50
As it sits as of now

0:00:36.00 --> 0:00:37.00 
it has 

0:00:37.30 --> 0:00:40.50
a short ram intake system

0:00:41.40 --> 0:00:44.50
a catback exhaust system

0:00:45.40 --> 0:00:48.60
lowering springs

0:00:49.40 --> 0:00:52.50
and a front strut bar.

0:00:53.50 --> 0:00:55.60
Once the weather warms up

0:00:56.00 --> 0:00:58.50
I'll be installing more parts

0:00:59.40 --> 0:01:01.30
front camber bolts

0:01:01.80 --> 0:01:03.60
rear camber arms

0:01:04.00 --> 0:01:05.90
a rear tie bar

0:01:06.30 --> 0:01:08.20
and a front lip.

0:01:10.60 --> 0:01:12.90
That's all I got for now

0:01:13.40 --> 0:01:15.80
thanks for watching.

0:01:16.10 --> 0:01:18.50
Here's a clip of what the car sounds like

0:01:27.30 --> 0:01:30.30
The end.